provenance.p:
In the s. XVI2
                             the manuscript was in the possession of an artist in Flanders. Jacobus van Suys bought the manuscript in 1573 in Gent (see the inscription on the flyleaf Sum Iacobi Danielis Filius Patris Nicolai Sussi. E pictoris pergula emptus mihi Gandaui Anno a Christo corporato MDLXXIII, Mense Ianuario 
                            ).
